This project contains a daemon and associated utility programs for controlling Home Automation nodes on an RS-485 network

Configure it by editing the Makefile. Adjust the install paths to suit your tastes.

Compile it by running:
  
  make

Install it by running:
  
  make install

The examples directory contains a sample han.conf and irr.conf. Use these as a starting point to create your own configurations.

Any feedback is welcome!

You can find the latest source distribution at:

https://github.com/hwstar/hand

For copyright notice and the authors see the source files.

